<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<style>
    * {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
  background-image: url('/images/userbg.jpg');
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  height: 100vh;
}

.profile-card {
  background-color: #fff;
  border-radius: 15px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  width: 350px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.profile-header {
  text-align: center;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #d9c80f);
  padding: 30px 20px;
  color: white;
}

.profile-img {
  width: 120px;
  height: 120px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin: 0 auto;
  border: 5px solid white;
}

.profile-img img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}

.user-name {
  font-size: 24px;
  margin: 15px 0 5px;
}

.user-role {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
}

.edit-btn {
  margin-top: 15px;
  padding: 8px 15px;
  border: none;
  background-color: #fff;
  color: #3498db;
  border-radius: 25px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

.edit-btn i {
  margin-right: 5px;
}

.edit-btn:hover {
  background-color: #3498db;
  color: white;
}

.profile-body {
  padding: 20px;
}

.profile-body h3 {
  font-size: 18px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.profile-body p {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #777;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.info {
  margin-top: 20px;
}

.info h4 {
  font-size: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.info p {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #555;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.info i {
  color: #3498db;
  margin-right: 10px;
}

.profile-footer {
  padding: 20px;
  text-align: center;
}

.logout-btn {
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border: none;
  background-color: #e74c3c;
  color: white;
  border-radius: 25px;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 16px;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

.logout-btn i {
  margin-right: 5px;
}

.logout-btn:hover {
  background-color: #c0392b;
}

</style>
<body>
    

 
  <div class="profile-card">
    <div class="profile-header">
      <div class="profile-img">
        <img src="images/me2.jpg" alt="Profile Image">
        </div>
      <h2 class="user-name">Mayank Pal</h2>
      <p class="user-role">Software Developer</p>
      <button class="edit-btn"><i class="fas fa-edit"></i> Edit Profile</button>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-body">
      <h3>About</h3>
      <p>I am Admin of this page. I am managing All the required things that any user required to be comfortabely use this plateform as their needs while creating it I mostly focus on user Friendly Interface and I wrote optimize code to enhancing it  </p>
      <div class="info">
        <h4>Contact</h4>
        <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> mayankpal199523@gmail.com</p>
        <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> 91+ 8860044187</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-footer">
        <a href="/login">
            <button class="logout-btn"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Logout</button>
        </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
